attributes.action: Stop all non-British citizens from voting in elections
attributes.background: We believe all non-British citizens, including illegal and legal migrants who are not British citizens, should not be allowed to bolster the vote of any representative in office, by any electoral party, and as such, should be barred from being on the electoral roll and being able to vote.
